ce" target="L01785">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 24. 7. [1908]</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01789">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 14. 9. 1908</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
